data.title: OpenAI's Big Rebrand: ChatGPT-Parent Wants To Reflect A 'More Organic' Future With New Logo, Typeface
data.description: OpenAI has unveiled a full-scale rebranding, introducing a redesigned logo and a new custom typeface called OpenAI Sans aimed at presenting a "more organic and human" identity.

data.title: Google AI's Search Revenue Matches Traditional Ads, Says Alphabet But There Is Rising Competition From OpenAI, Perplexity, DeepSeek
data.description: Alphabet Inc. revealed that its artificial intelligence-powered search features are achieving monetization rates comparable to traditional search results, marking a milestone in the company's AI strategy.

data.title: Apple Raises Monthly AppleCare+ Prices For All iPhones— And You Can No Longer Buy The Warranty Upfront In Stores
data.description: Apple has increased the monthly subscription cost for AppleCare+ across all iPhone models by 50 cents while discontinuing one-time purchase options in retail stores.

data.title: Gold Outshines Bitcoin As Trump's Gaza Plan, US-China Tensions Fuel Rally—Peter Schiff Calls It 'Extremely Bullish'
data.description: Gold prices surged to an unprecedented high of $2,849.05 per ounce on Wednesday, driven by renewed U.S.-China trade tensions and geopolitical uncertainties in the Middle East.
